# Datasets

> Standard library datasets.


<!-- <usage> -->

## Usage

``` javascript
var datasets = require( '@stdlib/datasets' );
```

#### datasets

Standard library datasets.

``` javascript
var d = datasets;
// returns {...}
```

<!-- </usage> -->


<!-- <examples> -->

## Examples

``` javascript
var getKeys = require( 'object-keys' ).shim();
var datasets = require( '@stdlib/datasets' );

console.log( getKeys( datasets ) );
```
